{"tid":1430571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[放映會] 今晚杏花村放映會，求推介位置","createTime":"2019-08-07T18:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T12:50:08.000Z","uid":294095,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"98a9552c0950ab0fe173649493e5057066b0c460","tid":1430571,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:52:04.000Z","msg":"🎥🎥18區連儂放映會- 杏花村站 🎥🎥<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>日期: 8月8日 星期四 <br />\n時間: 7:30 pm - 10:00pm <br />\n地點: 杏花村</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今次喺杏花村，就算幾藍都唔驚👊🏼👊🏼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YuOU5Rv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuOU5Rv.png&h=f5faa6f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7月30日喺西灣河，幾班人搞事我地唔驚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnoRoDg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnoRoDg.png&h=7f496abc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8月1日喺柴灣，橫風橫雨我地唔驚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OPy6cwN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOPy6cwN.png&h=ddbd333a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有經驗兼齊播放裝備? </span></span></strong><br />\n- 當日7:30pm 開始，喺杏花村自己選擇適合既地方放影<br />\n*記得喺TG Group 分享你既位置，一黎兄弟可以幫手睇住，二黎啲位冇咁易撞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>冇裝備但想現埸 Support?</strong></span></span><br />\n- 有額外兩套完整放映器材(想借用可以PM Admin)<br />\n- 保住兄弟安全<br />\n- 現埸派發傳單<br />\n- 現埸佈置連儂埸<br />\n<br />\n獲<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">得最新18區連儂放映資訊:</span></span></strong><br />\nFacebook Group: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/fb18districts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ffb18districts&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=a52e12c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/fb18districts</a><br />\nTG Group: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/18districts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F18districts&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJW9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=b3295078\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/18districts</a>"},{"pid":"fc21588693f4ffad380199731eda9c21978b64ae","tid":1430571,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:52:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fa15f809cb42ea488f85df46783a030cc6df6e","tid":1430571,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:55:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc78be9fcfcaaa86b465b42d25493080a57dad15","tid":1430571,"uid":259385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:06:01.000Z","msg":"杏花邨站一出兩邊都有樓梯 向上果邊係屋村黎 <br />\n唔肯定樓梯位置的兩邊牆比唔比你放映 <br />\n保安/狗鐵可能會怕阻到人<br />\n<br />\n然後行落去地面 M記再過少少係小巴站 <br />\n反方向又係入屋村的<br />\n<br />\n杏花新城有條天橋入屋村的 就係小巴站附近<br />\n<br />\n小巴果邊會多位少少 但入夜既人流一定會少過天橋<br />\n<br />\n唔好考慮巴士廠果邊 晚上鬼影都冇隻 再過就係Thei了"},{"pid":"6bf1ced5c4c0bf9830d8a038cc585c161494c2f6","tid":1430571,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:53:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b0cd69d07a410fbd7efa4b7df6efa6a25a7a3c","tid":1430571,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:40:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"469f3de4cc0583a871e8a9e1e1085e61a2449659","tid":1430571,"uid":294095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:41:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3